high_descs: Turn to the right, walk to the sink.
Take a plate out of the cabinet under the sink.
Turn to the left, walk to the stove, look at the microwave above the stove.
Place the plate in the microwave, heat the plate up for a few seconds, take the plate back out.
Turn to the right, walk to the sink.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the hot plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and face the sink on the left.
Open the bottom cabinet and take out the plate, shut the door.
Carry the plate and turn to the left and look at the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave and place the plate inside. Turn it on, then off and take the plate back out and shut the door.
Carry the plate and turn to the right to find the sink again.
Place the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a plate and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the sink on the left
Open the closet and remove the dish from the cupboard
Turn around and move to the oven on the right
Cook the dish in the microwave
Take the dish and move towards the sink on the left
Put the dish in the sink
anns.task_desc: Cook the dish in the cupboard and put it in the sink
